        "1996": {
          "vnum": 1996,
          "name": "Disused Stair",
          "description": "These stairs appear to have been little used in recent times, years of dust have accumulated upon them, and in places the hard rock is chipped and cracked. Each step is broad and flat, with a low riser, and the hall through which they descend is wide enough for several large men to walk abreast, likely to accommodate quick movement of forces into and out of the armory. You have lost 960 experience.",
          "grid_x": -1,
