        "1997": {
          "vnum": 1997,
          "name": "Ancient Armory",
          "description": "This huge chamber below the hill is filled with dozens of racks and long, low tables, almost all of which are completely bare. What remains are the leftovers of a great mustering of troops, and the only arms or armor they left behind were already unserviceable, and have grown ever more so with the passage of many harsh years.",
