        "1998": {
          "vnum": 1998,
          "name": "Guard Post",
          "description": "Tucked into the northern wall of the main armory is a small cubby, off to the side of the stairs. Ancient levers, now rusted beyond use, could once be used to drop twin gates, trapping any interlopers in a tight spot on the stairs just outside. Murder holes in the side wall allow spear and arrow access, to make short work of any imprisoned between the gates.",
          "grid_x": -1,
