        "1985": {
          "vnum": 1985,
          "name": "Cormanthus Hills",
          "description": "A trail through the grey hills above Cormanthus winds eastward deeper into the rolling terrain, and southwestward back toward the remains of the village. The trail is light and scarcly defined, but marked at intervals with skull- topped spears of petrified wood.",
