        "1986": {
          "vnum": 1986,
          "name": "Cormanthus Hills",
          "description": "The trail comes to a 'T' intersection amongst the hills here, near a steaming hot spring. Spearmarkers lead north, while the ruins of Cormanthus can be seen below and to the southwest. Just beside the spring, a pile of loose rubble looks to be all that is left of a small outpost.",
